title: "Articles | Finance Tools Hub 2026"
description: "Decision-focused guides on income, taxes, debt, retirement, and relocation."
canonical: "https://financetoolshub.net/articles/"
permalink: /articles/index.html
activeKey: ""
---

<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-emerald-50 border-b border-slate-200">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-14">
    <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-emerald-700">← Back to hub</a>
    <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-black">Articles</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600">Decision-focused guides on income, taxes, debt, retirement, and relocation.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
    {%- for art in articles | reverse %}
    <article class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 card-shadow flex flex-col">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-700 font-semibold">{{ art.publishedDate | longDate }}</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">{{ art.title }}</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600">{{ art.description }}</p>
      <a href="/articles/{{ art.slug }}.html" class="inline-flex mt-auto pt-4 text-emerald-700 font-medium hover:text-emerald-800">Read article →</a>
    </article>
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
